Novaria                COMPANIESSTRATEGYSTRATEGIC FACTORSTIMELINE OF GROWTHWhat We DoWHO WE AREOVERVIEWEXECUTIVE TEAMPRESS & EVENTSCONTACT US  A sum made greater In Precision Aerospace ComponentsFormed from the core belief that the greatest value comes from the strategic interplay of complementary parts, Novaria Group is a “sum made greater” by its aerospace operating companies. Investing and strategically operating in defined segments of the precision component sector, Novaria Group deploys over 70 years of Tier I and Tier 2 leadership experience to improve the operational and business capabilities and capital resources of small to mid-market manufacturing firms. A sum made greater In Precision Aerospace ComponentsFormed from the core belief that the greatest value comes from the strategic interplay of complementary parts, Novaria Group is a “sum made greater” by its aerospace operating companies. Investing and strategically operating in defined segments of the precision component sector, Novaria Group deploys over 70 years of Tier I and Tier 2 leadership experience to improve the operational and business capabilities and capital resources of small to mid-market manufacturing firms.    what’s in a name?Much like its investment and operational philosophies, the name Novaria is itself a powerful union of two elements—light and air—combined for deeper meaning. A nova occurs where a small star takes on matter from a much larger star, increasing its own brightness by up to one thousand times. An aria—literally translated from Italian as “air”—is a musical piece created as a showcase for individual talent.THE RESULTING NOVARIA IS A SIGNIFICANT COMPOSITION OF DISTINCTIVE PARTS, ALIGNED AS A NEW LEVEL OF INNOVATION AND VALUE.Fastening SystemsSurfaces & StructuresComponent Solutions ESNA The pioneer manufacturer of self-locking fasteners, specializing in the design of vibration and impact proof fasteners.ESNA Texas6625 Iron Horse Blvd.North Richland Hills, TX 76180ESNA Arka